The Turo marketplace has grown rapidly due to rental car shortages, and there are many new and inexperienced hosts on the platform. Don't jeopardize your travel plans by taking a chance on a host who may cancel your reservation at the last minute or provide a dirty or poorly maintained vehicle.  I have fulfilled over two thousand reservations, and have NEVER voluntarily cancelled someone's trip.  You can contact me any time if you need help with anything or have questions.  Count on my 5+ years of experience hosting on Turo and stellar reviews to make your trip a success!
